profile_positions.description:
My main responsibility is to create, support and modify sites of varying complexity. I've been doing development of the frontend as well as backend, and coding up creative graphic design to responsive HTML and CSS. During my time in the company I have successfully completed work on several projects, which resulted in satisfied customers.

Technologies used​: HTML5, CSS3, LESS, SASS, JavaScript, jQuery, AngulaJS, React Native Ajax, PHP, MySQL, cURL, JSON, SOAP, SSL, XML, Django, Ruby on Rails, Python, SSH, Unix, Docker, Git

Activities​:
•	Development of the entire websites, modules for already developed web sites, CMSs, web based databases;
•	Coding up from creative graphic design to responsive HTML & CSS (using LESS, SASS, media queries), CSS3 transitions;
•	Creation of WordPress plugins and templates;
•	JavaScript coding (including jQuery, AngulaJS, React Native);
•	Testing and verification of developed project.
•	Configuring of web­servers
•	Scrum development methodology
